%table#scoreboard.table.table-striped
  %thead
    %tr
      %th Name
      %th Chips
  %tbody
  - scoreboard.each do |data|
    %tr.player{:class => ("lost" if data[:lost_at] != nil)}
      %td= data[:name].slice(0,15)
      %td.chips
        != stack_display(data[:stack], false)
        = data[:stack] 
  %tr.info
    %td{:colspan=>2}
      Note: Rankings are based on chip count at beginning of latest round.
